        Why does Years & Years' Starstruck remix is not credited with Kylie as it was announced last week as new release? Does this week's climb counts on Kylie?

        Half Giant- Ethan

        31st May 2021
        4
        Vote score

        A) despite the remix topping the sales chart, it still isn’t as popular as the original
        B) our charts only tend to credit the original artist unless the artist rereleases the song under both artists names (note Confetti is still Little Mix despite the Saweetie remix)
        C) the remix streams & sales do count towards the song, so yes that is the root of the boost.
